<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[المعايرة]</span>: عايَرَ المكاييل وعاورها:<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>بمعنى.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
